{"tid":1988693,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[感動到嬲]我個藍撚到紅嘅老豆終於做選民啦","createTime":"2020-04-25T11:23:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-25T11:29:40.000Z","uid":202589,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"674d29abc69a5a78e64e2ec50841f9c10b5f38fa","tid":1988693,"uid":202589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T11:23:32.000Z","msg":"老豆放工返黎話做左選民 <br />\n我即刻開心左下 我問佢做返無端端去搞呢啲野<br />\n佢話唔會比班後生仔玩落去 又會今日見到啲垃圾後生仔做foodpanda 話啲巴基斯坦都有架單車仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我話人地預左做一世先買單車 啲後生仔做下part-time 要架單車黎做乜<br />\n<br />\n我老豆叫我唔好理咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我心諗:咁你又咁撚多事?<br />\n你地班垃圾要行路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家立會小心 我老豆呢啲柒頭都開始留意"},{"pid":"d91c47d7a7dfa543cf4ccd6d5652cc8bf70a4dd0","tid":1988693,"uid":353200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T11:27:47.000Z","msg":"到時記得請老豆返大陸玩洗走佢<br />\n呢度可能多幾百票， 手足可唔可以幫我定置頂<br />\n行動post-多一票就係多,DSE散場派選民登記表,唔想到時立法會選舉又輸幾票<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1988688\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1988688</a>"},{"pid":"dd91a279bbd1dcdaf994c46be68c532b79b93f4a","tid":1988693,"uid":146285,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T11:28:17.000Z","msg":"記得投票日安排好佢張身份證"},{"pid":"742b3d8d8e3aaf26de13705276a8baf871e7fcdf","tid":1988693,"uid":27605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T11:29:40.000Z","msg":"9月熱死辣辣去得狗屋報失返黎都濕撚曬啦"}]}